# Catch My Frame - Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in the values

# =============================================================================
# GOOGLE GEMINI API KEY (Optional)
# =============================================================================
# Required for AI Scene Detection feature
# Get your API key from: https://ai.google.dev/
# 
# Without this key, all other features will still work:
# - Manual frame capture
# - Interval capture
# - Pixel-difference detection
# - Time-range capture
# - All export options
#
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here

# =============================================================================
# NOTES
# =============================================================================
# 1. Never commit .env.local to version control
# 2. The app works 100% offline for local video files
# 3. AI features require an internet connection
